==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
Pinyin: sān k chǎnyè

===Etymology===
From the Japanese term "3K shigoto" (3K仕事, "3K jobs"), which stands for kitsui ([[きつい]] difficult), kitanai ([[汚い]] dirty) and kiken ([[危険]] dangerous).

===Noun===
'''3K[[產]][[業]]'''
#[[3D jobs]]: Dirty, dangerous, difficult jobs.

